- mobile: `font-size: 18, line-height: 26, letter-spacing: 0, weight: 500`

-- site-doc.component-property: `body`

Body property is used to add body content to heading components. Each heading
body is using common font-size, line-height and font-weight.

ðŸ”¶ Body text uses fastn default `$inherited.types.copy-regular` type.

- desktop: `font-size: 16, line-height: 24, letter-spacing: 0, weight: 400`
- mobile: `font-size: 16, line-height: 24, letter-spacing: 0, weight: 400`


